title: Jerry Parr, Secret Service Agent Who Helped Save Reagan, Dies at 85
text:
Jerry Parr, Secret Service Agent Who Helped Save Reagan, Dies at 85 
Published By: NYTimes - Today 
Mr. Parr was just feet away from the president when John W. Hinckley Jr. opened fire on March 30, 1981....
